modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod gives the player a chest of resources for the starter [quests](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-quests/). Read the dukes note to get a quality 3 stone age item to start with.

## Changelog

* Starter crate has been updated to b179 and added a quest to start with a quality 3 stone age item of choice also added some localization.
* Known incompatibilities with War3zuk AIO mod. You will need to rename Wolfbain5â€™s modlet by adding a z to the beginning and altering the entities.xml as a possible work around.

**[Download](https://github.com/wolfbain5/7dtd-a19/raw/master/wolfbain5%20-%20Starter%20Crate.rar)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/19825-wolfbain5s-a19-mods/).
